Enum Class LaneUseIndication

java.lang.Object
java.lang.Enum<LaneUseIndication>
us.mn.state.dot.tms.LaneUseIndication
All Implemented Interfaces:
Serializable, Comparable<LaneUseIndication>, Constable
public enum LaneUseIndication extends Enum<LaneUseIndication>
A lane-use indication is one of a set of possible states for a lane-use control sign. The ordinal values correspond to the records in the iris.lane_use_indication look-up table.
Author:
Douglas Lau
